          examples:

            name: ServiceType

          schema:
            type: string
            enum:

          examples:
            Returns the queue service.:
              value: default
        - description: REST Api Version.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the queue service.:
              value: 2015-12-01-preview
      responses:

          description: OK -- Queue service has been returned.

        - QueueServices
